{"type": "article", "id": 5615, "title": "Threem 便利贴", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-28T07:56:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234051ZEJXmhCqkR0wQ7uH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t成立于 2011 年的台北 GoGOLDFISH 设计工作室日前带来了一款 Threem 便利贴设计，以 6 张世界名画为主题，让生活那些大大小小的平凡杂事，透过名画前辈们的口信，变得更加有趣。Threem 便利贴采用 80 磅模造纸与大豆油墨支撑，每本 80 张，背后附有贴心的背架支撑，请用户可以轻松的将便利贴放置于桌面，不仅赏心悦目，更方便即使使用。想象坐在书桌前整天能与梵高、拿破仑或是戴珍珠耳环的少女对话这件事，还真是蛮有趣的，亦能为生活增添艺术氛围。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234048PxghqH1po6IG7SVR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234049ULm8hKuldOyNw2Hp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234049b4YnHF1McRhPmZCf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052340498E4pSwNVFsXmuDvo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234050FepXBSM9WwT1nOoc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234050eBQu3FDTMbJzLj7g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}